story: Pwnky, a creature from the Green of Inpinity Online, ventured through the digital realms with Light green eyes  eyes that sparkled with curiosity, a Mechanic body body that shimmered with the essence of creativity, and a Mechanic mouth  mouth that resonated with the voices of countless creators. On this journey, Pwnky's Ears bow ears fluttered in the electronic winds, and Hair on fire hair flowed like the rivers of code that shaped the landscape. Adorned with a Black hat hat crafted by the artisans of the net, Pwnky discovered the Glasses, a relic that could unlock new realms in this infinite universe.
description: a new Pwnkey with Green, Light green eyes , Mechanic body, Mechanic mouth , Ears bow, Hair on fire, Black hat, Glasses
